name: Endless Summer Game Jam Games
description:
This package has all of the games finished at the 2022 Endless Summer Game Jam at New England Institute of Technology on August 26 and 27. The five games are listed below.

  1. Enter the BoheMoth
  2. ex Worminator
  3. Garden of Eaten
  4. Inch by Inch
  5. Wormy To The Moon

The theme of the Game Jam was inch worm and as you can see it yielded some very interesting results. 

Enjoy!
